=== DRIFT_CACHE ===
# id: 13
# title: The Drift Cache
# chinese_title: 漂流箱
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A cargo pod, scarred by micrometeorite impacts, has lodged itself against the station's exterior docking ring. Its manifest tag identifies it as belonging to a Drift trader convoy lost three years ago. The pod's seal appears intact.

* [Crack open the pod]
  ~ gain_gold(40)
  "开" (kāi) — to open
* [Check the pod's beacon for owner data]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "主" (zhǔ) — owner, master
* [Salvage only the emergency supplies]
  ~ gain_item("stim_pack")
  "急" (jí) — urgent, emergency
* [Report the find to station authorities]
  ~ gain_radical("金")
  "金" (jīn) — metal, gold
